summer at mount rushmore in south dakota attended the dedication 
in a replica of the uniform roosevelt wore in the spanishamerican 
war 
nearly 4 million has gone into the reconstruction of the fort 
about 33 million came from the federal government and about 
500000 was provided by local supporters called friends of fort 
union 
